#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.102"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.102:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.102:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga"
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.102:0.3"
msgid "102. Bojjhaṅgasutta"
msgstr "102. Awakening Factors"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.102:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā tisso vijjā paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated "
"they fulfill three knowledges."

msgctxt "an10.102:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an10.102:1.3"
msgid ""
"Satisambojjhaṅgo, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo, "
"pītisambojjhaṅgo, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo, samādhisambojjhaṅgo, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "an10.102:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā tisso vijjā "
"paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"When these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they fulfill "
"three knowledges."

msgctxt "an10.102:1.5"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an10.102:1.6"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant recollects their many kinds of past lives. "

msgctxt "an10.102:1.7"
msgid ""
"seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ "
"sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr ""
"That is: one, two, three, four, five, ten, twenty, thirty, forty, fifty, a "
"hundred, a thousand, a hundred thousand rebirths; many eons of the world "
"contracting, many eons of the world evolving, many eons of the world "
"contracting and evolving. They recollect their many kinds of past lives, "
"with features and details."

msgctxt "an10.102:1.8"
msgid ""
"Dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe … yathākammūpage satte "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"With clairvoyance that is purified and surpasses the human, they understand "
"how sentient beings are reborn according to their deeds."

msgctxt "an10.102:1.9"
msgid "Āsavānaṃ khayā … pe … sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this "
"very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to the "
"ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an10.102:1.10"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā imā tisso vijjā "
"paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When those seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they fulfill "
"these three knowledges.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.102:1.11"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
